 to as the <em>maximum context size</em>. For applications using DistilBERT=
, the maximum context size is 512 tokens, which amounts to a few paragraphs=
 of text. As we'll see in the next section, a token is an atomic piece of t=
ext; for now, we'll treat a token as a single word. We can get a rough esti=
mate of tweet lengths per emotion by looking at the distribution of words p=
er tweet:</p>
