jp-InputArea-prompt">
</div><div class=3D"jp-RenderedHTMLCommon jp-RenderedMarkdown jp-MarkdownOu=
tput" data-mime-type=3D"text/markdown">
<p>One simple class of word tokenizers uses whitespace to tokenize the text=
. We can do this by applying Python's <code>split()</code> function directl=
y on the raw text (just like we did to measure the tweet lengths):</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
