enization Experiments<a class=3D"anchor-link" href=3D"https://courses.dalla=
rd.tech/ml/notebooks/transformers_classification/#exercise-2-tokenization-e=
xperiments">=C2=B6</a></h3><p>Understanding how tokenization affects model =
performance is crucial. Try the following experiments:</p>
<p><strong>Question 1:</strong> Load a different pre-trained model tokenize=
r (e.g., <code>bert-base-cased</code>, <code>roberta-base</code>, or <code>=
