 Use the <a href=3D"https://huggingface.co/models">Hugging Face Models Hub<=
/a> to find available models. What differences do you notice? How does case=
d vs uncased tokenization affect the output?</p>
<p><strong>Question 2:</strong> Experiment with the tokenizer's <code>paddi=
ng</code> and <code>truncation</code> parameters. What happens if you set <=
code>max_length=3D10</code> with <code>truncation=3DTrue</code>? Read the <=
a href=3D"https://huggingface.co/docs/transformers/main_classes/tokenizer">=
tokenizer documentation</a> to understand different padding strategies (<co=
de>max_length</code>, <code>longest</code>, <code>do_not_pad</code>).</p>
<hr>
