tput" data-mime-type=3D"text/markdown">
<p>The <code>AutoModel</code> class converts the token encodings to embeddi=
ngs, and then feeds them through the encoder stack to return the hidden sta=
tes. Let's take a look at how we can extract these states from our corpus.<=
/p>
