<h4 id=3D"extracting-the-last-hidden-states">Extracting the last hidden sta=
tes<a class=3D"anchor-link" href=3D"https://courses.dallard.tech/ml/noteboo=
ks/transformers_classification/#extracting-the-last-hidden-states">=C2=B6</=
a></h4>
</div>
</div>
