<p>We can see that <code>anger</code> and <code>fear</code> are most often =
confused with <code>sadness</code>, which agrees with the observation we ma=
de when visualizing the embeddings. Also, <code>love</code> and <code>surpr=
ise</code> are frequently mistaken for <code>joy</code>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"jp-Cell jp-MarkdownCell jp-Notebook-cell">
<div class=3D"jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex=3D"0">
