s<a class=3D"anchor-link" href=3D"https://courses.dallard.tech/ml/notebooks=
/transformers_classification/#defining-the-performance-metrics">=C2=B6</a><=
/h4>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"jp-Cell jp-MarkdownCell jp-Notebook-cell">
<div class=3D"jp-Cell-inputWrapper" tabindex=3D"0">
