jp-InputArea-prompt">
</div><div class=3D"jp-RenderedHTMLCommon jp-RenderedMarkdown jp-MarkdownOu=
tput" data-mime-type=3D"text/markdown">
<p>To monitor metrics during training, we need to define a <code>compute_me=
trics()</code> function for the <code>Trainer</code>.  This function receiv=
es an <code>EvalPrediction</code> object (which is a named tuple with <code=
>predictions</code> and <code>label_ids</code> attributes) and needs to ret=
urn a dictionary that maps each metric's name to its value. For our applica=
tion, we'll compute the $F_1$-score and the accuracy of the model as follow=
s:</p>
</div>
